    - default to "false" for the "APT::Get::Build-Dep-Automatic"
      option (follow debian here)
  * apt-pkg/pkgcache.cc:
    - do not run "dpkg --configure pkg" if pkg is in trigger-awaited
      state (LP: #322955)
