  * M68k config.guess patch. Closes: #88913
  * Bi-yearly test on OpenBSD and Solaris
  * Doc updates. Closes: #89121, #89854, #99671, #98353, #95823, #93057,
          #97520, #102867, #101071, #102421, #101565, #98272, #106914,
          #105606, #105377
